1
00:00:01,160 --> 00:00:02,840
(DOCTOR WHO THEME)

2
00:00:10,880 --> 00:00:13,360
Gentlemen, good news.

3
00:00:13,640 --> 00:00:17,600
My agents have procured the exact
security software that you requested,

4
00:00:17,920 --> 00:00:19,520
the very latest upgrade.

5
00:00:19,720 --> 00:00:22,320
I extracted it from the memory
of a Judoon trooper.

6
00:00:22,960 --> 00:00:26,400
Well, I say extracted.
It was quicker to take the whole brain.

7
00:00:26,960 --> 00:00:29,880
And to be honest,
I don't think he's going to miss it.

8
00:00:31,200 --> 00:00:32,480
Uh, uh, uh.

9
00:00:33,520 --> 00:00:35,280
A small matter of payment, I think.

10
00:00:37,040 --> 00:00:38,440
Delightful. (LAUGHS)

11
00:00:38,560 --> 00:00:42,160
Oh, I do enjoy sentient money.

12
00:00:42,640 --> 00:00:44,680
The way it wriggles.

13
00:00:45,800 --> 00:00:47,560
You'll find it in the frontal lobe.

14
00:00:48,080 --> 00:00:49,960
Should be quite easy,
there's not a lot in there.

15
00:00:51,960 --> 00:00:54,440
But all this to imprison one child?

16
00:00:56,320 --> 00:00:59,120
Oh, I know what you're up to.
I hear everything in this place.

17
00:01:00,040 --> 00:01:02,480
I even hear rumours about
whose child you've taken.

18
00:01:02,560 --> 00:01:04,040
Are you mad?

19
00:01:09,320 --> 00:01:12,960
You know the stories about the Doctor?
The things that man has done?

20
00:01:14,760 --> 00:01:17,400
God help us if you've made him angry!

